&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect and implement a data transformation strategy to enhance integrity, reduce risk, and improve scalability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead, develop, and mentor the Fund Accounting team, fostering an environment of growth and excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and execute process improvements within the Fund Accounting domain.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee operational activities, such as:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic management of third-party administrators through the NAV process, including internal shadowing and investor NAV estimations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supervision of year-end fund audits with external auditors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partnership with tax preparers for fund tax filings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Representation of Fund Accounting in regulatory reporting (e.g., PF, PQR, BE185) alongside Compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Management of special projects, including new fund launches and system integrations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build a team culture rooted in mentorship, intellectual curiosity, and impactful results.&lt;/li&gt;
