&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3-5+ years of professional software development experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience designing scalable and highly reliable software systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with Linux, distributed systems programming, and multithreaded programming&lt;/li&gt;
